1271
01:15:45.083 --> 01:15:47.335
<i>My main man, Lemon.</i>

1272
01:15:47.419 --> 01:15:51.005
<i>As I said before, one of the original</i>
<i>members of the</i> Def Poetry Jam.

1273
01:15:52.215 --> 01:15:53.925
